---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import TimeLineElement from "../components/cv/TimeLine.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Resume | Sena Lim" sideBarActiveItemID="cv">
  <div class="text-center mb-10">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-4-5xl font-bold">Sena Lim</h1>
    <p class="body-text text-gray-600">Product Lead | Building Inclusive, High-Stakes Platforms for Public Impact</p>
  </div>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
    <!-- Summary -->
    <section class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-md md:col-span-1">
      <h2 class="heading-2 mb-4">Summary</h2>
      Product Manager with 15+ years across mobility, agri-tech, and national platforms, including 7+ years delivering high-stakes, policy-constrained systems where trust, safety, and security are critical.
      <ul class="list-disc ml-5 space-y-2 body-text m-0">
        <li><b>Trust & Security:</b> Delivered a national EV system rebuild for 900+ vehicles and 30K users at BlueSG while ensuring service continuity and regulatory compliance. Cut KYC verification from 3 days to 5 seconds at Neuron with secure automation.</li>
        <li><b>Safety & Adoption:</b> Reduced safety violations by 12% and increased vehicle take-up by 10% at Neuron through CV-based parking guidance. Scaled adoption to 3M+ low-digital-confidence farmers in 12 countries at Yara via SMS-first onboarding and inclusive UI design.</li>
        <li><b>Leadership & Delivery:</b> Built and mentored a 5-person product team at BlueSG; boosted squad velocity by 37% at Yara. Maintained delivery momentum by embedding async planning, backlog reviews, and trade-off reviews.</li>
        <li><b>Stakeholder Alignment & Technical Fluency:</b> Aligned 9 C-suite leaders on post-acquisition roadmap at BlueSG and co-developed MVPs with farmers across 3 continents at Yara. Led API integrations, secure flows, and IoT rollouts across engineering, design, policy, and city teams.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- Experience -->
    <section class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-md md:col-span-2 md:row-span-4">
      <h2 class="heading-2 mb-4">Experience</h2>
      <div class="time-line-container grid gap-y-8">
        <!-- Sabbatical -->
        <TimeLineElement title="Sabbatical (Learning & Exploration)" subtitle="Sep 2024 - Present">
        Focused on structured learning in AI and exploring a hobby as a potential business.
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 mt-2 m-0">
            <li><b>AI & Automation:</b> Built my first portfolio site end-to-end (VPS setup, domain purchase, GitHub template customization, and iteration with ChatGPT Codex). Completed AI automation classes and created 3 n8n workflows plus a Langflow-powered RAG chat assistant — applying AI concepts through working prototypes <a href="https://senalimlab.com/ai_projects/">(View AI Projects)</a>.</li>
            <li><b>Entrepreneurship:</b> Explored baking as a business avenue. Studied baking science, developed healthier recipes, and applied product thinking to test differentiation and market potential.</li>
          </ul>
        </TimeLineElement>

        <!-- BlueSG -->
        <TimeLineElement title="BlueSG | Product Lead" subtitle="Apr 2023 - Aug 2024">
          Led product strategy and delivery for Singapore’s national EV car-sharing platform (900+ EVs, 1,500+ lots, 30K+ active users), ensuring service continuity and regulatory compliance.
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 mt-2 m-0">
            <li>Maintained service continuity during live system rebuild by scoping critical journeys and leading backend, API, and IoT delivery with engineering, design, policy, and ops teams.</li>
            <li>Unlocked faster decision-making and roadmap clarity by aligning 9 C-suite and department leads through post-acquisition workshops using JTBD and Kano.</li>
            <li>Drove >20% adoption in a new user segment by launching a planner-focused mobility package based on user behavior, data insights, and competitor analysis.</li>
            <li>Avoided launch delays and user disruption by preparing fallback flows, toggles, and comms triggers across critical modules.</li>
            <li>Maintained steady delivery and reduced blockers by hiring, building and mentoring a 5-person product team and embedding async planning, backlog reviews, and trade-off discussions.</li>
          </ul>
        </TimeLineElement>

        <!-- Neuron -->
        <TimeLineElement title="Neuron Mobility | Senior Product Manager, Rider Core Experience" subtitle="Apr 2023 - Aug 2024">
          Owned end-to-end rider experience across AU, NZ, CA, and UK, including for 10% of riders with mild disabilities, through IoT-integrated software and compliant city launches.
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 mt-2 m-0">
            <li>Cut identity verification time from 2–3 days to under 5 seconds by launching secure KYC automation with Jumio; improved trust and reduced manual review load.</li>
            <li>Reduced safety violations by 12%, cut rebalancing workload by 18%, and increased vehicle take-up by 10% in A/B zones by launching CV-based parking guidance with ops teams and city councils.</li>
            <li>Improved scan success rate by 23% in low-light conditions by analysing user journey data and auto-enabling torchlight in the end-of-ride flow.</li>
            <li>Delivered on-schedule rollouts in AU, NZ, and CA by adapting product behavior to local regulations and aligning with legal, ops, and city teams to meet approval timelines.</li>         
          </ul>
        </TimeLineElement>

        <!-- Yara -->
        <TimeLineElement title="Yara International | Senior Manager / Product Owner" subtitle="Oct 2018 - Jun 2022">
          Led digital platforms for smallholder farmers, driving inclusive adoption across 12 countries globally in low‑connectivity, compliance‑sensitive environments.
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 mt-2 m-0">
            <li>Scaled inclusive adoption to 3M+ farmers across 12 countries by designing onboarding for users with low digital confidence, including SMS-first access, multi-language support, and larger UI for older users.</li>
            <li>Improved retention by 18% by launching advisory tools and peer content tailored to how farmers learn and trust information.</li>
            <li>Co-developed weather and loyalty MVPs with farmers by involving them as research panelists in 60+ co-design and field testing sessions across India, Thailand, and South Africa.</li>
            <li>Enabled smoother rollouts and reduced rework by aligning squads across APAC, LATAM, and EMEA on onboarding readiness, regulatory compliance, and localisation needs.</li>
            <li>Increased team delivery velocity by 37% by embedding prioritisation and backlog review rhythms across 4 cross-regional product squads.</li>
          </ul>
        </TimeLineElement>

        <!-- GfK -->
        <TimeLineElement title="GfK | Digital Project Manager, Digital Media" subtitle="Apr 2016 - Sep 2018">
          Part of the Digital Media product team managing a SaaS media measurement platform for APAC, supporting Digital Partnerships’ multi‑million‑dollar deals (SGD 1M+ each) with global media clients.
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 mt-2 m-0">
            <li>Delivered IMDA’s $2M Smart Nation audience insights platform, enabling data‑driven campaign planning and public policy decisions.</li>
            <li>Enhanced data trust and adoption by improving panel representativeness and closing demographic gaps across APAC markets.</li>
          </ul>
        </TimeLineElement>

        <!-- Appvantage -->
        <TimeLineElement title="Appvantage Asia | Digital Project Manager" subtitle="Aug 2014 - Mar 2016">
          Managed Daimler’s APAC SaaS automotive platform across 12 markets, enabling vehicle showcasing and financing (pricing, downpayment calculators) for prestigious automotive clients.
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 mt-2 m-0">
            <li>Managed Daimler’s APAC SaaS automotive dealer and financial platform across 12 markets.</li>
            <li>Boosted online‑to‑offline conversion by 23% through multi‑market SaaS rollout and localized digital sales journeys.</li>
          </ul>
        </TimeLineElement>

        <!-- Earlier Technical Roles -->
        <TimeLineElement title="Appvantage Asia, Codigo, GlobalITCreations | Technical Lead / Mobile Developer" subtitle="April 2009 - July 2016">
          <ul class="list-disc ml-6 space-y-2 m-0">
            <li>Delivered native iOS/Android and IoT‑integrated solutions for public‑sector and automotive clients, forming a solid technical foundation for multi‑system product leadership.</li>
          </ul>
        </TimeLineElement>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Education -->
    <section class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-md md:col-span-1">
      <h2 class="heading-2 mb-4">Education</h2>
      <div class="time-line-container grid gap-y-8">
        <TimeLineElement title="BS Computer Science" subtitle="University of Wollongong, 2012" />
        <TimeLineElement title="Diploma in Digital Entertainment Technology" subtitle="Nanyang Polytechnic, 2009" />
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Certifications -->
    <section class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-md md:col-span-1">
      <h2 class="heading-2 mb-4">Certifications</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-5 space-y-2 body-text m-0">
        <li>
          <a href="https://www.scrum.org/certificates/320451" target="_blank">Professional Scrum Owner™ II (PSPO II)</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="https://www.credly.com/badges/eb116a77-4b84-4635-aa59-723acb14d905?source=linked_in_profile" target="_blank">Professional Scrum Master™ I (PSM I)</a>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <!-- Skills -->
    <section class="rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-md md:col-span-1">
      <h2 class="heading-2 mb-4">Skills</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc ml-5 space-y-2 body-text m-0">
        <li>APIs & IoT</li>
        <li>Multi‑System & Live‑Ops Delivery</li>
        <li>Agile Product Delivery (JIRA, Confluence, Miro)</li>
        <li>Data Analytics (Amplitude, Mixpanel, Power BI)</li>
        <li>Generative AI, Agentic AI & Workflow Exploration</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
